  <style>
    html, body, .fake-shell {
      height: 100%;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
    }

    .fake-shell {
      z-index: -2;
    }

    .fake-topbar {
      align-items: center;
      background-color: #ffec8b;
      border-bottom: 1px solid gold;
      display: flex;
      height: 50px;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .fake-topbar-side {
      margin: 0 15px;
      display: flex;
    }

    .big-loading-indicator {
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
      border-radius: 10px;
      height: 35px;
      width: 180px;
    }

    .small-loading-indicator {
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
      border-radius: 7.5px;
      height: 20px;
      margin-left: 15px;
      width: 60px;
    }

    .cloudonaut {
      left: calc(50% - 216.5px);
      position: absolute;
      top: calc(50% - 150px);
    }

    .cloudonaut-image {
      background-color: white;
      transform: translateY(-50px);
      transition: transform 1.25s ease;
    }

    .cloudonaut-image.loaded {
      transform: rotateY(180deg);
    }

    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .cloudonaut {
        visibility: hidden;
      }

      .big-loading-indicator,
      .small-loading-indicator {
        visibility: hidden;
      }
    }
  </style>
  <div class="fake-shell">
    <div class="fake-topbar">
      <div class="fake-topbar-side fake-topbar-left">
        <div class="big-loading-indicator"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="fake-topbar-side fake-topbar-right">
        <div class="small-loading-indicator"></div>
        <div class="small-loading-indicator"></div>
        <div class="small-loading-indicator"></div>
        <div class="small-loading-indicator"></div>
        <div class="small-loading-indicator"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cloudonaut">
    <img class="cloudonaut-image" src="data:image/png;base64,">
  </div>
  <script>
    var interval;

    function toggle() {
      if (window.state) {
        return clearInterval(interval);
      }

      var cloudonaut = document.querySelector('.cloudonaut-image');
      cloudonaut && cloudonaut.classList.toggle('loaded');
    }

    document.onreadystatechange = function() {
      if (document.readyState !== 'interactive') {
        return;
      }

      toggle();
      interval = setInterval(toggle, 1250);
    };
  </script>
